Introduction

U-Know, known as Yunho, is a South Korean singer and actor under SM Entertainment. He is a member of the male duo TVXQ!.

He released his first Japanese solo mini-album, "U KNOW Y" on July 8, 2015, and made his Korean solo debut on June 12, 2019, with the mini-album "True Colors".
